R: potassium chloride 1.2 mol/l; Sol. 2: ammonium hydrogen difluoride 100 mmol/l; Sol. 4: sodium sulphite 600 mmol/l; Sol. 6: sodiumhypochlorite <1% active chlorine neodisher Ma: 0.35%\n
